The program features the participation of Czech jazz artist Karel R<0xC5><0xAF><0xC5><0xBE>i<0xC4><0x8D>ka and his Celebration Jazz Mass.
In the evening will be held in the places of celebration of the Municipal House in Vynohrady the concert "Students of Velvet", in which university choirs will participate, including the choir of the Carolina Unversity.
