The fall in economic activity has generated, until November, a steady increase in unemployment in the state, according to the National Institute of Statistics and Geography, the rate of state unemployment during the first three quarters of the year was observed a thousand thousand accelerated, as from January to March average 55 thousand 053 percent of people in the state were unemployed, with a rate of 4.53 percent of the Population Economically Active, and a 6.
Lower liquidity
